long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Fancy text generator is a cool chrome extension which helps the users to generate the stylish fancy texts which can be easily copied and used anywhere. This Chrome extension has multiple types of options available which generates the fancy texts, cool texts, bold texts, italic texts, bubble texts and many more other fonts.

This font generator has also some special features like generating the unlimited stylish fonts and texts. The Best thing is it also quickly copies the texts or fonts which are generate.

Types of Fonts Generated by this fancy text generator

Mirror Text Generator - This can Turn the text reversed and upside down at the same time!.
Striped Text Generator - It Converts the Font to different Text Styles.
Underline text Generator- This converts the Normal Text into Underline Text.
Bold Text Generator - It converts the Normal Fonts into Bold Text.
Flip Side Text Generator - This type of Font generator Usually Flips the Text.
Luni Bubbles Text Generator - It converts the Font in very uniue style
